	 ('5b03966a1acd4d5bbd67237b','1','Captain America The Winter Soldier','https://www.themoviedb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/tVFRpFw3xTedgPGqxW0AOI8Qhh0.jpg','https://coconut88.quickconnect.to/drive/d/s/qlufMI5lQSDdNPE3HlXtnFJrIGcGUenr/1XaNa5vhimzK3XWq9beLo9x0nJ1MUEsb-bblAiCze6wk','',40000,'After the cataclysmic events in New York with The Avengers, Steve Rogers, aka Captain America is living quietly in Washington, D.C. and trying to adjust to the modern world. But when a S.H.I.E.L.D. colleague comes under attack, Steve becomes embroiled in a web of intrigue that threatens to put the world at risk. Joining forces with the Black Widow, Captain America struggles to expose the ever-widening conspiracy while fighting off professional assassins sent to silence him at every turn. When the full scope of the villainous plot is revealed, Captain America and the Black Widow enlist the help of a new ally, the Falcon. However, they soon find themselves up against an unexpected and formidable enemy—the Winter Soldier.',2014,136,'Anthony Russo','Chris Evans,Scarlett Johansson,Sebastian Stan',77,'on','2021-10-30 02:31:49','2021-10-30 02:31:49'),
	 ('5b03966a1acd4d5bbd67237c','1','Deception','https://www.themoviedb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/fRQ3JV67ADyTrRNyXqefqJkJsD4.jpg','https://coconut88.quickconnect.to/drive/d/s/qlvXqpxSYUjsPDaFwsH9v6EH5JnL4cOY/9VqMSQ3_jZuGH_Z5WahHSBLw9oiFa55Z-rb2AgMXe6wk','',40000,'Cameron Black is the worlds greatest illusionist. At least, thats what people used to call him—before his greatest secret was exposed and his career destroyed. Even worse, Cameron has good reason to believe this was no accident.',2018,42,'Chris Fedak','Jack Cutmore-Scott,Ilfenesh Hadera,Lenora Crichlow',78,'on','2021-10-30 02:31:49','2021-10-30 02:31:49'),
	 ('5b03966a1acd4d5bbd67237e','1','Fifty Shades Freed','https://www.themoviedb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/9ZedQHPQVveaIYmDSTazhT3y273.jpg','https://coconut88.quickconnect.to/drive/d/s/qmUf4NcrkGfjixeo3VouAlzgabjEeCWs/47G7JQnVLdckhHDOzeGPn7lq36aMsOQO-Pr_AsR7f6wk','',40000,'Believing they have left behind shadowy figures from their past, newlyweds Christian and Ana fully embrace an inextricable connection and shared life of luxury. But just as she steps into her role as Mrs. Grey and he relaxes into an unfamiliar stability, new threats could jeopardize their happy ending before it even begins.',2018,105,'James Foley','Dakota Johnson,Jamie Dornan',67,'on','2021-10-30 02:31:49','2021-10-30 02:31:49'),
